 145:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) TriggerCallback                   : TIM Trigger Callback.
 146:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) TriggerHalfCpltCallback           : TIM Trigger half complete Callback.
