3028:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_tim.c ****   * @note   Switching from Center Aligned counter mode to Edge counter mode (or reverse)
3029:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_tim.c ****   *         requires a timer reset to avoid unexpected direction
