7707:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_tim.c ****   * @brief  Configure the TI1 as Input.
7708:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_tim.c ****   * @param  TIMx to select the TIM peripheral.
