7715:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_tim.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
7716:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ICSELECTION_DIRECTTI: TIM Input 1 is selected to be connected to IC1.
7717:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ICSELECTION_INDIRECTTI: TIM Input 1 is selected to be connected to IC2.
