7720:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_tim.c ****   *          This parameter must be a value between 0x00 and 0x0F.
7721:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_tim.c ****   * @retval None
7722:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_tim.c ****   * @note TIM_ICFilter and TIM_ICPolarity are not used in INDIRECT mode as TI2FP1
